metadata.name: Amcor plc
metadata.description: Amcor plc develops, manufactures, and sells various packaging products for food, beverage, pharmaceutical, medical, home and personal care, and other consumer goods end markets worldwide. It operates through two segments, Flexible Packaging and Rigid Packaging. The company provides flexible packaging products, rigid containers, specialty cartons, and closures. The company is headquartered in Zürich, Switzerland.
